Nigerian sex therapist and entrepreneur, Hauwa Saidu Mohammed popularly known as Jaruma, has demanded a refund of the monetary gift given to Big Brother Naija Star, Natasha Akide aka Tacha, Music executive Uni Franklin and other BBN stars. She made the demand in a post via her official Instagram page on Thursday, reacting to thereport of Adam Namadi, son of former Vice President Namadi Sambo, who received a refund from delegates after losing the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) House of Representatives ticket for Kaduna North Federal Constituency. She wrote, “Jaruma was there for u when u needed money. Jaruma was good to u. Jaruma helped u. Can u now do the same for Jaruma? Please, I need u now pls return my N250,000. -Advertisement- “Any one I have ever sent money to please return back my money. 1. Naijabrand chick N500,000 2. Naijabrand chick N1,000,000 3. Naijabrand chick N250,000 4. Askdamz N250,000 Ubi Franklin 1,000,000 5. Fybcraft N500,000 6. Esther BBN N500,000 7. BBN the real Ella N2,000,000 8. Me Jollof, N1,000,000 Theisaacola N250,000 Theisaacola N500,000 Theisaacola N500,000 Tianna staff N1,000,000 Tacha N1,800,000 Tacha N,400,000 Tacha N500,000.”